gw.api.heatmap

Class LatLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.heatmap.LatLong

  • public class LatLong
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a geographic point with a (latitude, longitude) pair with an associated database entity key. Latitude corresponds to y and longitude corresponds to x, the reverse of the conventional (x,y) notation. Both are in degrees (-90 to +90, -180 to +180).

    Subclass LatLong to associate additional data with the point.

    Author:
    jfehrle
